content: Tell me a joke about Starcraft.

Sure! Here's one: 

Why did the Protoss go to the doctor?

Because he was feeling a bit... Zerg-y! 

Get it? Zerg is one of the races in Starcraft, known for being insectoid and, well, not exactly the picture of health. So, the Protoss, who are more advanced and elegant, would probably feel uncomfortable or sick if they started to feel "Zerg-y." 

Hope that made you laugh!
